These are the server rules

- Do not argue
- Do not post invite links, external links (.co.uk etc)
- Do not post data about a customer
- Do not post un suitable pictures
- Use the correct channels
- Be friendly, welcome each other
- Follow rules. Simple, right?

These rules were last updated by **Joshia** at 29/09/2018
